data.description: Kelly's Landing- Mt Holly/Stanley area. Beautiful home with fenced backyard on cul-de-sac lot. Everything has been polished and painted to sparkle like new. New plush carpet upstairs, solid surface on main level. Large open kitchen with dining area and additional morning room (would make a great office space or play area). Granite countertops in kitchen and baths. Ample kitchen cabinets and pantry. Three spacious bedrooms upstairs with large loft area. Primary bedroom features lovely on-suite bath and walk-in closet. Ceiling fans in all rooms. Extra wide garage with storage. Shows like new. Neighborhood pond and lighted sidewalks. USDA, FHA, and Conventional Eligible.
